      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "STARLIGHT TWIX (3) has an excellent record over this course and distance having never missed the placings in five starts, including three wins and two placings. Scored by 5 lengths last time (17.42) in a LS6 over 297m at this track. Looks suited here and rates on top. INCREDIBLE GLORY (1) missed the frame latest but had been racing well prior to that including a Grade 5 win two back (17.51) at Mandurah. Has the ability and expected to do much better. BRUISER MY UNCLE (2) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at this track behind Gold Smirch (17.61) in a Grade 4/5. Has the pace to be prominent. Can measure up. SURELY (7) jumped best and was never headed last time. Will be thereabouts.",
